 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003ESmall and medium merchants in large cities are eager for differentiation, customer loyalty and efficient access to online users. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EZeerca offers an attractive marketing solution for urban merchants in terms of economic conditions and customer interactivity.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EZeerca has launched a mobile solution, which allows merchants to issue tailor-made offers to nearby customers, and allows customers to request selected offers from merchants. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EAdditionally, Zeerca is currently developing, together with the MIT Media Lab, a Big Data solution that will provide the merchants with an accurate pattern of their customers\u2019 habits, lifestyle, time location and place location in order to better segment offers.\u003C/p\u003E",
